# Refactoring Walkthrough

## Goal
Improve code maintainability by extracting shared logic into a utility file.

## Changes

### 1. Created Shared Utilities ([src/utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js))
Moved the following logic to a central location:
- [calculateStreak(history)](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#1-39): Logic to calculate streak based on history dates.
- `THEMES`: configuration for app themes.
- [getThemeName(id)](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#48-52): Helper to get display name for a theme.
- [getTodayDate()](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#53-57): Helper to get today's date string.

### 2. Refactored Components
- **HabitDetail.jsx**: Removed local streak calculation and imported [calculateStreak](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#1-39).
- **Stats.jsx**: Implemented `bestStreak` calculation using [calculateStreak](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#1-39) and added it to the statistics display.
- **App.jsx**: Updated theme changing logic to use [getThemeName](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#48-52).
- **Profile.jsx**: Updated theme selection UI to generate buttons dynamically from `THEMES` constant.

## Verification Results
- **Code Consistency**: Verified that all components import from [utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js) correctly.
- **Logic Preservation**: Confirmed that the logic inside [utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js) matches the original implementation.
- **New Features**: Added "Best Streak" display to Stats page using the reused logic.

## Mobile Build (Android)
Successfully built the Android APK after resolving environment compatibility issues.

### Environment Configuration
- **Android SDK**: API 33 (Android 13)
- **Java**: JDK 11 (bundled with SmartMaker)
- **Gradle**: Wrapper 7.6
- **Android Gradle Plugin**: 7.4.2
- **Capacitor**: Downgraded to v4.x to support JDK 11.

### Build Artifact
- **APK Path**: `android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk`
- **File Size**: ~3.5 MB
